import React from 'react'
import Color from './Color'

const colorInfo = [
    {
        title: Green,
        background: 'green',
        image: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'
    },{
        title: Blue,
        background: 'blue',
        image: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'
    },{
        title: Yellow,
        background: 'yellow',
        image: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'
    },{
        title: 'Red',
        background: 'red',
        image: 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRA1A1R6gih7fuwDfycsrqLjamIsJUQ79UqYQdkTlSft7WWvMFTqw'
    }
]

const ColorBox = () => {

    const mappedColors = colorInfo.map((color)=>{
        return <Color title={color.title} background={color.background} pic={color.image} />
    })
    return (
        <div id='colorContainer'>
            {mappedColors}
        </div>
    )
}

export default ColorBox
